+ !*************************************************************************
+ !*
+ !* NAME : MTH_MulMatrix  -  Multiple Matrix
+ !*
+ !*     void   MTH_MulMatrix(MthMatrix *a, MthMatrix *b, MthMatrix *c)
+ !*
